  introDialogue:
  - You made it.
  - 'ActionAid has arrived and

    provided supplies to

    outlast the flood.'
  - "Thanks to ActionAid's incredible\nefforts, people all across\nthe world have
    access to food,\nwater, shelter, sanitary products, \nand medicine during\nhumanitarian
    emergencies. "
  - 'To learn more about

    ActionAid''s work, visit their

    website by clicking
    the

    button on the main menu

    or visiting their website at

    www.actionaid.ie.'
